                    <height>
                      <measure type="height" quantity="8.75" unit="in">8 3/4</measure>
                    </height>
                    <width>
                      <measure type="width" quantity="5.5" unit="in">5 1/2</measure>
                    </width>
                  </dimensions>
                </extent>
                <foliation/>
                <collation>
                  <p>The quires were 15 in number. Originally they were signed with both letters and arithmetical figures (see fol.<locus from="99a" to="99a">99 a</locus>,<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܓ</foreign>
                    <!-- ADD MISSING ARABIC -->).</p>
                </collation>
                <condition>
                  <list>
                    <item>
                      <p>Some of the leaves are slightly stained and torn, especially foll.<locus from="1" to="1">1</locus>,<locus from="9" to="9">9</locus>,<locus from="30" to="30">30</locus>,<locus from="69" to="70">69, 70</locus>,<locus from="128" to="129">128, and 129</locus>.</p>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                      <p>Quires<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܙ</foreign>and<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܚ</foreign>are missing. Quires are now marked with letters only.</p>
                    </item>
                  </list>
                </condition>
              </supportDesc>
              <layoutDesc>
                <layout columns="1" writtenLines="23 27">
                  <p>There are from 23 to 27 lines in each page.</p>
                </layout>
              </layoutDesc>
